mil.nga.giat.geowave.vector.wms

Interface DistributableRenderer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable

    public interface DistributableRenderer
extends Persistable
    This interface is used to perform rendering within tablet servers. The persistable object can be serialized and transported to an Accumulo Iterator and the iterator can render each object to a series of images (one per style in the case of multiple styles and an additional one for labels to adhere to layering rules). The client of this iterator can then composite the images from the tablet server.
